    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "INTERNATIONAL AIR MARINE TERMINAL, LA GUARDIA FIELD, NEW YORK.\nPhoto shows the first trans-Atlantic flight (the Yankee Clipper) leaving the air base\nMarch 31, 1940. The administration building is at the left. The clipper was en route\nto Lisbon, Portugal, carrying nine passengers and 5,260 pounds of mail."
    ],
